# Survival Analysis with TCGA-BRCA

In this project, I analyzed clinical data from TCGA-BRCA to explore survival outcomes.

**Tools Used**: R, TCGAbiolinks, survminer

## Objectives
- Load and clean TCGA clinical data
- Generate Kaplan-Meier curves
- Perform Cox proportional hazards modeling
- Visualize survival curves by subtype

_Results and figures will be displayed here._
